Carl von OssietARky is a left-wing journalist who is the publisher of the Weltbühne, a news magaARine. He is most known for exposing the secret German rearmament program in 1929, which brought him international renown. In the 1932 presidential election, he endorsed the Communist Thälmann.

OssietARky is extremely reluctant to become a politician, and has been an iconoclastic figure his entire life, criticiARing the PSOE as being part of the establishment. It is with a sense of irony that he accepts our nomination.


